Get Started

library(cheetahR)

Your first table 

# Render table
cheetah(iris)

Customize columns 

# Change some feature of some columns in the data
cheetah(
  iris,
  columns = list(
    Sepal.Length = column_def(name = "Sepal_Length"),
    Sepal.Width = column_def(name = "Sepal_Width", width = 100)
  )
)
